        <Parent_String>variegated marble [300011533], marble by color or pattern [300011483], marble (rock) [300011443], metamorphic rock [300011437], rock (inorganic material) [300011692], inorganic material [300010360], materials by composition [300212963], materials (substances) [300010358], Materials (hierarchy name) [300010357], Materials Facet [300264091]</Parent_String>
